name: DOGGO
description: DOGGO is a project about growing brand identity in the attention economy. DOGGO aims to take the attention economy by the horns and join the new advent of brand identity tokens to develop into a widely known and intensely loved digital identity not unlike Mickey Mouse, or Pokemon. DOGGO is just the start of the artist's artistic universe, and the more support DOGGO gets, the more robust the ecosystem and art will become.
